Belgium to Get EU Warning Over Government Formation, Soir Says

-- B y   A o i f e   W h i t e
-- 
2011-09-01T06:05:51Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-09-01/belgium-to-get-eu-warning-over-government-formation-soir-says.html
Belgium  may this month receive an
official warning from the European Commission over the country’s
failure to form a government or make economic reforms, Le Soir
 reported , citing a European Union official it didn’t identify.  The EU will tell Belgium that it needs to make important
structural reforms to encourage economic growth that can’t be
decided by an interim government, the newspaper said. The EU
will publish its warning in the week starting Sept. 12, Le Soir
said.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Aoife White in Brussels at 
